{"tid":16238,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（地獄泡菜國）青年成「七抛」世代","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T16:13:12.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96a495b15324fc4f5f1de1cc2b9aaf7a2657f684","tid":16238,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"2010年，南韓網民創造了一個新詞語，將韓文지옥（地獄）與조선（朝鮮）組成新字「헬조선（地獄朝鮮）」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n現在，這個用語已被廣泛應用於描述當今南韓生活，以表達對社會已經完全無希望，含着「金鎖匙」出世的富二代永遠贏在起跑線。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n據南韓《中央日報》，三分之一的SKY（南韓三大名校分別為首爾大學、高麗大學及延世大學，合稱SKY）人文學科畢業生無業，現代集團更只錄取理工科學生。<br />\n<br />\n可以想像非SKY畢業生情況更苦，2013年南韓20歲世代年輕人聘用率，僅為55.8%。台灣有「22K現象」，南韓也有「88萬圜世代」（很多未能晉身公務員或大企業的青年只能拿取約6000港元月薪）。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「三拋世代」遂成為潮語。所謂「三拋」即放棄戀愛、放棄家庭、放棄生育，還有「五拋」放棄人際關係及買樓，以及「七拋」連夢想及希望都捨棄。<br />\n<br />\n節錄自12月號《信報財經月刊》"},{"pid":"88860ed678fe27d3d0a3ec74e7460f6178b544ad","tid":16238,"uid":43454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"有人講返呢個topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c087f686546c06a1e75c3bd62568718d6c0f29","tid":16238,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"香港都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f583861ba086f2f4418a745a2ad1685a91397f32","tid":16238,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人講返呢個topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今期信報月刊既報導黎"},{"pid":"d6c92721f5cd749501a764e6535816313c7fa402","tid":16238,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"香港都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c35229d5ae2888167b2f19c547d231370dcbfc","tid":16238,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"香港入唔到8大都已經係七拋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做狗另計"},{"pid":"eed72c48e17281463098fa204286d26f412063de","tid":16238,"uid":43454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effb192c62300401df4e44658e415c71806b0607","tid":16238,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}